title: Israel's Netanyahu scraps African migrant relocation deal
text:
Israel's Netanyahu scraps African migrant relocation deal 10:14am EDT - 01:52 
Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu said on Tuesday he was cancelling an agreement with the U.N. refugee agency to relocate thousands of African migrants, bowing to right-wing pressure to scrap the deal. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
